cellsegkit (vendored under shared/cellsegkit/)
  Cell segmentation + export toolkit from the previous-generation project
  "Cryobiology III": https://github.com/nazarzharskyi/cryobiology3
  Author: Fedir Yarovyi. License: MIT.
  Used here for: deliverable mask rendering/export (bake) and the segmentation
  model factory (apps/segmentation). The interactive editing/grouping logic of
  Mask Picker is original to this project (see docs/architecture/13).
  The upstream MIT license text ships inside shared/cellsegkit/.

Segmentation models (invoked via their own packages; respective licenses apply):
  - Cellpose            (cyto2 / cyto / nuclei)
  - InstanSeg           (instanseg, instanseg-torch)
  - Ultralytics YOLO    (yolo11_*)
  - Segment Anything (SAM) / CellSAM

Model weights (custom Cryobiology IV finetunes, ~1.8 GB) are NOT distributed in
this repository; obtain them separately (see README) and place in cryobiology4/weights/.
